Package com.android

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Animal
    simple class to create Animals Animal class does NOT have it's own equals method, so it will use the equals() method from the Object class so Animals will said to be equal only if two references point to the same Animal
    Examples
    class that hold examples that illustrates some of the common concepts of Collections
    Human
    class to create Human Objects This class overrides the equals() method, so it has it's own equals class.
    Main
    class that contains our main method
    MyList
    this is just a dummy class to show all the methods contained in the List Interface and any class that implements this interface has to override these methods.
    MyList2
    class that implements Comparable
